routeFacts.name: East Coastway
routeFacts.description: East Coastway is the fifth British route arriving in TSW 2020. It features the 23-mile line between Brighton and Eastbourne whilst also including the 7 mile Branch Line from Lewes to Seaford. It features both passenger services with the BR Class 377/4, BR Class 313 and freight with the BR Class 66.
